replies.msg:
Jorginho, <br />
<br />
 &ldquo;We are playing with more long balls, more runs, less short passing. I try to do what the coach wants. Yes, it has changed a little bit but the mentality is the same, to press the other team and try to have control of the match&rdquo;

Asked whether, he was now Chelsea&rsquo;s designated spot-kick man, Jorginho laughed: &ldquo;You will have to ask Frank!&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Another of this season&rsquo;s penalty takers, Ross Barkley, was on the pitch and Tammy Abraham also appeared interested but Jorginho revealed: &ldquo;He came up and said, &lsquo;You are taking the penalty?&rsquo; and I said, &lsquo;yeah&rsquo;, and so he said &lsquo;OK&rsquo;.&rdquo;

